{
  "stem": "56.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think that my sister went to see [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Voik, ?] because she came home and she said to my dad that [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Voik ?] said that there's nothing he'll be able to do, because he won't even be in the ghetto at this time, because this is a different department of Germans who's going to come in.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were called the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[GERMAN] is like somebody comes suddenly and falls on you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he sent word that my father should hide me and my brother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we had a basement in the floor, and my father fixed it up a little bit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, when the Germans come, the two of you will go into this basement.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How big was the basement?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it wasn't big.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was about, I would say, five by five, the most.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was in the ground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived on the main floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was in the ground.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Polish people always had a place like that to keep-- it was a storage place to keep food that shouldn't spoil, because it was always cold down there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my father fixed it up a little bit, that we could--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He put a couple stools there, that we could sit on the stools, and a jar of water.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we used to have drills, and used to go in there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everything went fine until the day came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when the day came, I didn't want to go in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I just refused to go in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was so scared, because I heard stories that if they found someone who was hiding, they shoot them immediately, that they put a gun to their head and shoot them.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
